blueprint.description:
Circular design for 90 Military science per minute.

Full spaghetti and no regard for space efficiency. Producing at ratio from plates, bricks and coal.

Can be made before unlocking military science with available techs by that moment.

blueprint.description:
Vanilla Green (Logistics) Science complex to make 90 items per minute from raw materials. 

Made with the intention of doing some nice spaghetti, but keeping efficiency in mind.

The design principle is to have the science generation in a circular shape with necessary production in a column below.

Can be made with everything you have available before unlocking green science.
blueprint.label: [item=logistic-science-pack][virtual-signal=signal-1]
